019-08-09T17:35:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f4f1465c05e4392a83485c310e4bf1a6e3011cc9","tid":1438184,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:37:32.000Z","msg":"大家加油"},{"pid":"99bfe1574f09bc442b07ffb30cecc3a3c3d19365","tid":1438184,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:38:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家覺得加返deadline升級好唔好？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n依家情況同上一個月差多<br />\n又係做好多嘢令到<span style=\"color: red;\">行動失去咗個目的</span>同埋冇時限搞到好似好迷失方向，和理非定勇武定包圍，行動上都係冇共識<br />\n加返deadline有好處<br />\n1.重申五大訴求，目標清晰，行動出師有名<br />\n2.訂立短中期行動計劃，例：今個禮拜和理非回合，唔回應就下個禮拜升級勇武行動<br />\n3.有計劃容易整合文宣<br />\n4.自己人有清晰目標，喺啲狗每日shift focus之下叫人專注返都易啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得 和理非&gt;deadline&gt;勇武升級 嘅抗爭概念<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431556</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34f40fcdb43b69e5ee910d0b7e5e429ae2adb829","tid":1438184,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:41:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"500019ad15955d4ad345767e8660d960efa51603","tid":1438184,"uid":105693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:41:27.000Z","msg":"香港人，頂硬上<br />\n冇得退啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccd0b8877296d988d2675838c2b264daa1ef3c3","tid":1438184,"uid":189961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"推 振一振士氣 真心只要我地自己唔分化自己 任何人出咩招都分唔到我地 希望每一個香港人都意志堅定 都係嗰句 核彈都唔割呀屌你個閪 香港人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass